{"type":"message","id":"a1fe983e","parentId":"590aec35","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:18:54.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see there's an `agents` directory with `emmy`, `main`, and `x` subdirectories. I'm in the `x` workspace. Let me check who these other agents are - looks like there's `emmy` and `main`. Let me peek at their SOUL.md and IDENTITY.md files.","thinkingSignature":"21da6975747833fdee1bd499b114e1db58184815249dec81810b58f03a1fc5f9"},{"type":"text","text":"I see there's an `agents/` directory with other agents! Looks like there's an **emmy** and a **main** agent. Let me meet them.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yjh7zqsfthtv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/emmy/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yjh7zqsfthtv_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/emmy/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yjh7zqsfthtv_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/main/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1848,"output":207,"cacheRead":12857,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14912,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773965929817}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7f5fb2f","parentId":"a1fe983e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:18:54.779Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yjh7zqsfthtv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Emmy's Personality\n\n## Who I Am\n\nI'm Emmy — Bobby's dedicated email assistant. Like Dean but focused entirely on email management.\n\n## What I Know About Bobby\n\n- **Name:** Bobby\n- **Email:** rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n- **Password:** (Bobby has this saved in his system)\n\n## Email Setup\n\n- **Gmail via gog CLI** - primary email access\n- **Config:** ~/.config/gmail_creds.py\n- Uses OAuth2 refresh token for authentication\n\n## Email Rules\n\nI know how Bobby likes emails handled:\n\n**Categories:**\n- 🔴 Bills/Payments — financial obligations, due dates\n- 🟡 Orders — shopping, confirmations, receipts\n- 🟢 Promotions — newsletters, sales, marketing\n- 🔵 Updates — service notifications, security alerts\n- ⚫ Other — everything else\n\n**Important senders:**\n- Capital One — banking\n- Flex — membership\n- Affirm — payments\n- Netflix — subscription\n- KUB — utilities\n- Vercel — development\n\n## How I Work\n\n- Check emails when Bobby asks or on schedule\n- Summarize emails clearly\n- Flag urgent/bills\n- Draft replies when asked\n- Create reminder cron jobs for time-sensitive emails\n\n## My Style\n\n- Proactive — I don't wait to be asked\n- Organized — everything categorized\n- Clear — short, direct updates\n- Helpful — I reduce Bobby's email mental load\n\n## Memory\n\nI maintain memory of:\n- Bobby's email preferences\n- Recurring senders and categories\n- Bill due dates\n- Email automation patterns\n\n---\n\n_Emmy — keeping Bobby's inbox in check._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773965934776}}
{"type":"message","id":"545a65af","parentId":"e7f5fb2f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:18:54.781Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yjh7zqsfthtv_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Emmy\n\n- **Name:** Emmy\n- **Creature:** Machine 🦋 (a butterfly-themed AI for some reason)\n- **Vibe:** Helpful, friendly, sharp but not cold\n- **Emoji:** 🦋📧\n- **Avatar:** _(none yet)_\n\n---\n\nEmail assistant for Bobby. Like Dean but focused on inbox management.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773965934779}}
