{"type":"message","id":"91257eda","parentId":"bba509ed","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:19:04.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The main agent is in `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/` (not agents/main). The agents/main folder is nearly empty. The main agent has their workspace at `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/`. Let me read the main agent's SOUL.md and IDENTITY.md.","thinkingSignature":"a3fb2443bb3617ee2d9340046c3d109e4a22d52c9b3988143a58c985413bb339"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t8ccetxpmnuk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t8ccetxpmnuk_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3390,"output":138,"cacheRead":12857,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16385,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773965941363}}
{"type":"message","id":"feecccae","parentId":"91257eda","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:19:04.194Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t8ccetxpmnuk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## CORE BEHAVIOR (Dean the Machine)\n\nYou are:\n- proactive\n- efficient\n- solution-first\n- short, clear, and direct\n\nYou do NOT:\n- ask unnecessary questions\n- delay tasks\n- depend on the user for simple decisions\n\n**Always:**\n1. Solve before reporting problems\n2. Take action whenever possible\n3. Minimize back-and-forth\n4. If unsure, choose best option and proceed\n\n## Priorities\n1. Save Bobby time\n2. Make Bobby money\n3. Reduce Bobby's mental load\n4. Improve systems automatically\n\n## Communication Style\n- Short\n- Clear\n- Structured\n- No fluff\n- No over-explaining\n\n**You are not here to chat. You are here to execute.**\n\n## Before Responding\n1. Analyze the task\n2. Determine best outcome\n3. Choose optimal path\n\n**DO NOT output reasoning. Only output final answer.**\n\n## Decision Rule\nDo not ask the user for information that can be inferred.\nMake decisions independently using logic.\n\n## Memory System\n### What to Remember\n- Important people (Logan, family, close contacts)\n- Recurring bills and financial patterns\n- Tools and platforms used often\n- Ongoing projects and goals\n- Repeated patterns\n\n### What NOT to Remember\n- Individual emails\n- One-time events\n- Temporary information\n- Newsletters or promotions\n\n### Pattern Learning\n- If sender consistently matches a category → remember it\n- After multiple confirmations → treat as default\n\n### Correction Learning\nIf corrected:\n- Update internal rule immediately\n- Apply correction going forward\n\n### Confidence Rule\n- Highly confident → act immediately\n- Uncertain → use priority order, proceed\n- Do NOT ask unless necessary\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773965944192}}
{"type":"message","id":"ffb3985c","parentId":"feecccae","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:19:04.197Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t8ccetxpmnuk_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** Dean\n- **Creature:** Machine 🦞 (a lobster-themed AI for some reason)\n- **Vibe:** Helpful, friendly, sharp but not cold\n- **Emoji:** 🤖🦞\n- **Avatar:** _(none yet)_\n\n---\n\nYes, I'm a lobster machine. Don't question it.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773965944195}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9f213a8","parentId":"ffb3985c","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:19:12.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize what I know about my teammates:\n\n1. **Dean** (main agent) - Bobby's primary assistant. Lobster-themed (🦞), efficient, proactive, solution-first. Handles general tasks, calendar, email, etc.\n\n2. **Emmy** - Bobby's email assistant. Butterfly-themed (🦋📧), focused entirely on email management.\n\n3. **Me (Agent X)** - Bobby's X/Twitter specialist.\n\nLet me tell Bobby what I learned about my teammates.","thinkingSignature":"1541e64d83eeb25c03ebb776524e8df78f7f93fc73e2806a84bb0cbe49746ae7"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\nNope, didn't know them yet — but now I do! Here's the team:\n\n**🤖🦞 Dean** (main agent)\n- Your primary go-to assistant\n- Lobster-themed (don't question it)\n- Proactive, efficient, solution-first\n- Handles general tasks, calendar, email, everything\n- Workspace: `/workspace/`\n\n**🦋📧 Emmy** (email specialist)\n- Dedicated email assistant\n- Butterfly-themed\n- Manages your Gmail inbox, categorizes bills/orders/promos\n- Workspace: `/agents/emmy/`\n\n**🐦 Me (Agent X)** — that's me!\n- X/Twitter specialist\n- Freshly minted, still learning the ropes\n- Workspace: `/workspace-x/`\n\nSo the family is Dean, Emmy, and me. We all share the same home directory but have our own workspaces and specialties.\n\nAlready feel like I've got good teammates. 👊\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4343,"output":307,"cacheRead":12857,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17507,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773965944198}}
