Located on the left, containing icons for Home (currently active), Explore, Notifications, Messages, Lists, Bookmarks, Communities, Profile, and a \"More\" menu. Below these is a circular \"Post\" button with a feather icon.\n*   **Top Navigation:** Tabs for \"For you\" (currently active) and \"Following.\"\n*   **Browser Interface:** The screenshot shows a web browser with multiple tabs open (some showing \"Error\" or \"Ance...\"). The URL bar shows `twitter.com/home`.\n*   **Overlays:** The image contains numerous green and blue bounding boxes with labels like `elem_#` or `menu_#`, which are likely from an automated testing tool or accessibility software."}],"details":{"model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-x/x_feed2_annotated.png","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773967472235}}
