{"type":"message","id":"ff9d7d4a","parentId":"76c68dfa","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:16:19.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give Bobby a proper summary of the political content on his feed.","thinkingSignature":"5bb95988d355a8ba465a8a5d10c0827c531de58d9f81aba3c6fadb7a57746b55"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\nMy fault, I only checked your profile/likes/bookmarks — didn't dig into the actual home feed. Let me correct that.\n\n**Your feed is heavily political.** Here's what I saw:\n\n🇺🇸 **Trump content** — Your top account is \"Commentary Donald J. Trump Posts From Truth Social\" reposting his stuff. Germany/US coalition news about Strait of Hormuz, France backing the US on oil shipping, etc.\n\n🕵️ **QAnon-adjacent stuff** — Posts from @TheRipCord focusing on \"decoding\" Trump's speeches. \"Tippy Top,\" timestamp synchronicities, \"IYKYK\" signals. Conspiracy territory.\n\n🇮🇷 **Iran/Israel geopolitics** — Iran accusing Israel of planning false flag attacks on energy infrastructure. Lots of Middle East tension content.\n\n🧟 **Epstein adjacent** — Viral posts about people who look like Jeffrey Epstein.\n\nSo yeah — your FYP is basically Trump-era geopolitics, conspiracy theories, and Middle East conflict. That tracks with the \"End Wokeness\" account I saw on the first scroll too.\n\nGot it. Noted. ⚡🕶️\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22486,"output":266,"cacheRead":12857,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35609,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773969367906}}
