{"type":"message","id":"a6f9887f","parentId":"8c15a183","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:26:19.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants his X account to be about everything he does - all his hobbies and projects. Not just one niche. Let me think about what I know about him:\n\n1. Music + media creation\n2. Faceless YouTube Shorts with AI automation\n3. AI/local LLMs (ollama)\n4. Crypto/prediction markets (Polymarket)\n5. DeFi\n6. Content creation\n7. OpenClaw (he's using it, researching it)\n\nSo his account should be a mix of:\n- AI automation content creation\n- Music production\n- YouTube Shorts progress\n- Crypto/prediction markets\n- Maybe some OpenClaw stuff\n- His experiments and projects\n\n\n- \"Creator: music + media. Building faceless YouTube Shorts with AI automation.\" - this is already him\n\nI should help him understand that being multi-passionate is actually his strength here. The key is tying everything back to a consistent theme - maybe the through-line is building in public, experimenting with tools, or the creator journey itself. I can offer to help him develop a content strategy that showcases his personality and projects without forcing everything into one niche.","thinkingSignature":"735293da91793e2da958a1d5118ac1c6f9ccb2720a513129be60c9a4c28c2952"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\nThat's actually better. Niche accounts die. Personal brands with a clear person behind them — that's what people follow.\n\nBased on what I've seen, here's what's on your plate:\n\n**Your universe:**\n- 🎵 Music production\n- 🎬 Faceless YouTube Shorts + AI automation\n- 🤖 Local LLMs / AI tools\n- 📊 Crypto + prediction markets (Polymarket, DeFi)\n- 🧠 Building things in public / experiments\n\n**The angle:** You. A guy in Knoxville building cool shit with AI and documenting everything — music, content, crypto plays, whatever you're tinkering with that week.\n\n**How to structure it:**\n\n- **~60%** — Your actual work (what you're building, what worked, what flopped, tools you're using)\n- **~20%** — Opinions/takes on AI, crypto, content creation\n- **~20%** — Personal (Knoxville life, what you're listening to, random shit)\n\n**The vibe:** Transparent builder. Not a guru — a guy actually doing it. That's who people connect with.\n\n**What I can do:**\n- Draft posts in your voice\n- Find relevant trending topics to jump on\n- Help you batch content\n- Monitor your mentions/engagement\n\nYou got the content. We just gotta package it right. Want me to start drafting some posts? ⚡🕶️\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":535,"cacheRead":9670,"cacheWrite":32863,"totalTokens":43160,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773969958279}}
