{"type":"message","id":"3ad7476a","parentId":"af0978c2","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:26:58.259Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby's telling me he's got no filter on politics either. He speaks his mind. This is important context for his brand - he's a free thinker, no-bullshit, speaks-his-mind type. This tracks with the political content I saw on his feed - Trump commentary, QAnon-adjacent stuff, etc.\n\nI should update my understanding of his brand and maybe update the MEMORY.md to reflect this. And let him know this is good - authentic voices with opinions cut through the noise.","thinkingSignature":"47d4ab5904a5f91495f6a381bf2cb0190e8ffcfb2813b5e409275864c0c73e4f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gqq0cclcgker_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-x/MEMORY.md","oldText":"## Political Content (observed on X feed)\n- Trump commentary accounts (reposting Truth Social content)\n- Germany/US coalition news regarding Strait of Hormuz/Iran\n- QAnon-adjacent content (pro-Trump \"Tippy Top\" conspiracy theories)\n- Iran/Israel geopolitical tensions\n- Viral political gossip (Epstein-related)","newText":"## Political Content (observed on X feed)\n- Trump commentary accounts (reposting Truth Social content)\n- Germany/US coalition news regarding Strait of Hormuz/Iran\n- QAnon-adjacent content (pro-Trump \"Tippy Top\" conspiracy theories)\n- Iran/Israel geopolitical tensions\n- Viral political gossip (Epstein-related)\n\n## Bobby's Style\n- Speaks his mind, doesn't give a fuck\n- No filter on politics or anything\n- Authentic, not a guru — just a guy doing cool shit"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":334,"cacheRead":42764,"cacheWrite":191,"totalTokens":43381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773970008322}}
