{"type":"message","id":"7ec24195","parentId":"694ecdf1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:27:09.055Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me give him a real response about this. This is actually a strength - people follow people with opinions. It's boring when everyone's neutral.","thinkingSignature":"d4e649fad17195455aca27bd2389836af6d7772930e072b7e04c71cf90594ec5"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\nThat's actually a strength. Look around at the biggest accounts on X — they all have opinions and post with conviction. Neutral accounts get ignored. The ones who say \"this is wrong, this is right, here's why\" are the ones who build real audiences.\n\nYou already proved it — your feed is full of political commentary and you're not hiding from it. Lean into that.\n\n**Bottom line on brand:**\n\n> \"Bobby. Knoxville. Building things with AI. Music. Crypto. Says what he thinks. Doesn't care if you agree.\"\n\nThat's your brand. The political shit, the AI experiments, the DeFi plays — it's all you. Post it all.\n\n**One word of advice:** Don't try to be controversial for engagement. Just be honest. People can tell when you're performing vs when you're real. You've got the latter down.\n\nWant me to help you draft some posts that sound like you? That's where I come in. ⚡🕶️\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":24011,"output":234,"cacheRead":19406,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43651,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773970018310}}
