{"type":"message","id":"10fe2364","parentId":"23a5cdb4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T17:04:24.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It says \"the chat couldn't be resolved\" - the Telegram contact needs to be reconfigured. The reminder failed to deliver because it couldn't resolve the Telegram chat. This is a configuration issue.\n\nThe error says \"the chat couldn't be resolved. The reminder will need to be delivered manually or the Telegram contact needs to be reconfigured.\"\n\nThis is weird because the Telegram does work - Bobby messages me on Telegram and I can receive and reply. But maybe the outbound sending to Telegram is failing for some reason.\n\nLet me just try sending a message directly to see if it works.","thinkingSignature":"e89a4c5d5e5d34fea3529be9754b63c6d1f4aa2a54e415ee9c5631a6a2a674e3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qxephytd2rkg_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","target":"8212808444","message":"1PM reminder test — cleaning your X posts today ⚡🕶️"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":28784,"output":189,"cacheRead":19444,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48417,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774026259294}}
