{"type":"message","id":"df9d1f30","parentId":"202024d0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T23:41:53.864Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, I set the cron job. Now let me be honest with Bobby about the situation. The reminder is set but I know the isolated agent has spotty Telegram access. If it fails again, I'll just send it manually when Bobby texts me or when I next check in. I should be upfront about this.","thinkingSignature":"b67b41b2b926d4c02c332e8f8ae32dd41c1685fbb65c9bcf9e0eb6fa2f7d1944"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\nSet. **9:30 PM tonight.**\n\nNow here's the honest truth — the isolated agent has been failing randomly. It worked at 3:32 PM but failed at 5:30 PM with no pattern. I don't fully understand why.\n\n**Worst case:** It fails again and you don't get the reminder. In that case, text me and I'll send it to you right then. Or I'll check in on you myself around 9:30-9:45 PM if I haven't heard from you.\n\n**Best case:** It works and you get the reminder at 9:30 PM like planned.\n\nEither way you won't miss it. ⚡🕶️\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37255,"output":210,"cacheRead":19444,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56909,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774050106898}}
