{"type":"message","id":"88bc36d7","parentId":"e7eed20b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:24:33.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK it's set for 9 PM. But Bobby is frustrated with the cron failures. Let me also note in my memory to check at 9 PM and send manually if needed. But wait - if I check and the cron already sent it, I'll double send. \n\nLet me just wait and see what happens. If the cron fires, Bobby gets a text. If not, he texts me and I send it immediately. That's the safest approach.\n\nActually, the issue might be that the isolated agent is spawning fresh each time and losing connection to Telegram. Maybe I should try to keep the session alive? I don't think I can though.\n\nLet me just trust the cron this one time. If it doesn't fire, Bobby will text me and I'll send it immediately. I already committed to that.","thinkingSignature":"ad6b8ea894f16426dbe8ad7ef726d7904676a928e130f887b54ca041b076a34b"},{"type":"text","text":"\nSet. 9 PM. \n\nIf it doesn't fire, text me and I'll send it immediately. I got you. ⚡🕶️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":47227,"output":193,"cacheRead":19743,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774139066349}}
