{"type":"message","id":"9959db7b","parentId":"60fe38e3","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:48:50.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby's asking me to stop sending confirmation messages. He's getting tool result outputs that show things like \"messageId: 120, chatId: 8212808444\" - those are the tool results, not messages I send. He's seeing the raw tool output and doesn't want it.\n\nBut those are just OpenClaw tool results - I can't really suppress those. The tool result for `message send` shows delivery status automatically.\n\nActually, I think Bobby might be referring to the confirmation messages I was sending AFTER the reminder - like \"Sent reminder to Bobby on Telegram\" etc. But looking at the conversation, I don't think I was actually sending those confirmation messages - I was just responding to tool results.\n \nLooking back at what Bobby's actually seeing - he's getting the raw tool results like \"ok: true, messageId: 120, chatId: 8212808444\" which are just OpenClaw system outputs. There's no way for me to suppress those since they're automatic system responses, not messages I compose. The \"Sent Telegram message to Bobby\" text he mentioned earlier sounds like it might have been a system-generated confirmation or possibly from a different context I'm not quite recalling. I'm realizing I was actually doing that earlier—sending follow-up confirmation messages like \"Reminder sent!\" after using the message tool, which is just cluttering the conversation. I should just stick to sending the actual reminder without the extra \"done\" message afterward. I'll stop sending those extra confirmation messages and just let the tool result speak for itself. I also need to clean up those lingering cron jobs before wrapping up.","thinkingSignature":"41580b2e068b8b04e0146323f72812fbb96eabb7004c66ad69b6c5d8f186b7fc"},{"type":"text","text":"My bad — I won't send those anymore. Just the reminder itself, nothing else. ⚡🕶️\n\nLet me also clean up all those old failed cron jobs so you're not getting any more spam from me.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ism8bznr41x6_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":394,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":66865,"totalTokens":67351,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774144106563}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd77b349","parentId":"9959db7b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:48:51.025Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ism8bznr41x6_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7ebeb660-c8cb-4322-9977-b9ac7bb24c20\",\n      \"agentId\": \"finn\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:finn:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"finances-tonight-10pm\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774138866247,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774138866247,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"at\",\n        \"at\": \"2026-03-22T02:00:00.000Z\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Hey Bobby! 👋 Still owe me those updated finances. No rush, just whenever you get a sec 🧊💸\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774144800000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n      \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773960428074,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774142865705,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773961081922\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are Emmy, Bobby's email assistant. Read ~/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/EMAIL_ASSISTANT_SKILL.md to see all email rules. Then check for ALL UNREAD emails in Bobby's Gmail inbox using the Gmail API with ~/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/emmy_gmail.py. For each unread email: 1) Read it FULLY, 2) Label using the rules, 3) Apply priority (Urgent/Important/Low), 4) Mark as READ (remove UNREAD label), 5) Do NOT star emails. Send a summary to Telegram in THIS EXACT FORMAT ONLY (no narrative, no explanations, just the format below):\\n\\n📬 NEW MAIL (X new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Brief snippet]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Brief snippet]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Brief snippet]\\n\\nIf no unread emails, send ONLY: No new emails! 🎉\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774146447802,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774142847802,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 17903,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"2afe9643-ca26-4e70-9d6a-da18a8c44028\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Morning Brief\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773809061618,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774103247667,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"30 5 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are Bobby's morning assistant. Run the morning brief skill located at ~/.openclaw/skills/morning-brief/SKILL.md. Follow it exactly. Deliver the brief to Telegram chat 8212808444. Each section should be sent as a SEPARATE message, ONE AT A TIME. Sections: Header, Weather, Bible Verse, Emails (yesterday+today via Gmail API), Calendar (7 days), Reminders, Suggestions. Do NOT include X/Twitter section. Do NOT skip any sections. Use MiniMax-M2.7 model. Send each section one by one via message tool.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774171800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774103210578,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 37089,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"51e7a4a4-4419-4fc4-b97a-3d7b882dd638\",\n      \"agentId\": \"finn\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:finn:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"finances-update-reminder-8am\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774073643758,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774114358610,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"at\",\n        \"at\": \"2026-03-22T12:00:00.000Z\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Hey Bobby! You said you'd send me your updated finances. Ready when you are 👍🧊💸\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120,\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774180800000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"73548199-c8d2-4df3-b576-40764ea53480\",\n      \"agentId\": \"rex\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:rex:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Weekly XVideos Cleanup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774137592975,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774137592975,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 10 * * 0\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Hey Bobby! It's time for your weekly XVideos folder cleanup. Check ~/Desktop/XVideos/ and see if there's anything you want to delete or archive. Also see if there's anything worth keeping in XVideoTranscripts/.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774188000000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"102438fe-4d8f-422c-96b0-693e02a172a3\",\n      \"agentId\": \"yoyos\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:yoyos:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"TikTok personas reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774073617161,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774114356430,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"30 10 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"TikTok persona reminder: Bobby wanted to discuss building AI-generated TikTok personas for making money. Continue the conversation about niche selection, persona creation system, tools, and content production workflow.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774189800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774103400008,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 54506,\n        \