{"type":"message","id":"37eb730b","parentId":"241bfd2e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:20:10.583Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4bytuddfulno_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the screenshot, here is a detailed description of Bobby Galletta’s X (Twitter) profile:\n\n*   **Display Name:** Bobby Galletta ⚡ (includes a lightning bolt emoji).\n*   **Username:** @BobbyGalletta.\n*   **Verification Status:** Next to his name is a blue checkmark icon with the text \"Under review.\"\n*   **Bio:** \"building cool shit. music. ai. whatever i feel like.\"\n*   **Location:** A United States flag emoji (🇺🇸).\n*   **Bio Link:** [linktr.ee/rtg.bobby](https://linktr.ee/rtg.bobby)\n*   **Join Date:** Joined August 2025.\n*   **Post Count:** The profile indicates he has **5 posts**.\n*   **Following/Followers:** 92 Following, 19 Followers.\n*   **Header Image:** A dark, moody, cinematic photograph showing a profile view of Bobby looking down at a guitar. The background is blurry and dark, suggestive of a music studio or stage environment with structural elements and faint lights.\n*   **Profile Picture:** A circular portrait of a young man with short dark hair, smiling and wearing a white t-shirt.\n\n**Overall Profile Appearance:**\nThe profile is set to \"Dark Mode.\" At the top, there is an \"Edit profile\" button, indicating this is the account owner's view. Below the bio and stats, there is a navigation bar with the following tabs: **Posts** (currently selected), **Replies**, **Highlights**, **Articles**, **Media**, and **Likes**. \n\nThe most recent visible post is dated September 15, 2025, promoting a single titled \"On My Body.\" The post includes a space-themed graphic of the single's cover art and several music-related hashtags. Interestingly, the dates shown on the profile (Join date: August 2025; Post date: September 2025) are in the future relative to the system clock shown in the Mac menu bar (March 22)."}],"details