{"type":"message","id":"74ca28dc","parentId":"37eb730b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:20:20.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the profile now. Let me give Bobby feedback:\n\n1. Name: \"Bobby Galletta ⚡\" - looks good, matches what he wanted\n2. Bio: \"building cool shit. music. ai. whatever i feel like.\" - that's exactly one of the options I gave him, perfect\n3. Location: 🇺🇸 - he put a flag emoji instead of \"Knoxville, TN\" - could be more specific but it's fine\n4. Link: linktr.ee/rtg.bobby - that's his existing linktree link\n5. Header image: Dark moody guitar photo - that's a great header, very music-focused\n\n\n6. Posts: He's got 5 posts visible, mostly old ones like the \"On My Body\" promotion from September and some older content from before he cleaned up\n\nThe profile looks solid overall. The main thing is he's still got that old promotional post sitting there that he said he deleted - it's still showing up in his feed. The bio and header image are working well, but he's got some cleanup to do on the posts themselves. The header image works well for now, and that September post about \"On My Body\" needs to go since he's cleaning everything up. The bio's already set exactly how I suggested it. He mentioned cleaning replies too, so let me verify he actually deleted those as well.","thinkingSignature":"2aba8ceffcba9685f2a25cb572da7a97d90b3b6b89221338d29036894a044560"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tkhsbnjfta8q_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"peekaboo app quit --app \"Google Chrome\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":60823,"output":320,"cacheRead":19753,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80896,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774153210590}}
