{"type":"message","id":"872b0799","parentId":"90241c89","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:20:30.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give Bobby feedback on his profile.","thinkingSignature":"c054a7121ae603a72cbb52913b858205c50e76e44e7e9de1879c667f00a6840f"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\nLooking good. Here's the rundown:\n\n✅ **Name:** \"Bobby Galletta ⚡\" — clean, that's you\n✅ **Bio:** \"building cool shit. music. ai. whatever i feel like.\" — perfect, exactly what you picked\n✅ **Header image:** Dark moody guitar photo — actually really good, music vibe hits immediately\n✅ **Location:** 🇺🇸 — you went with the flag instead of Knoxville. That's fine but \"Knoxville, TN\" would be more specific and start conversations about where you're from\n⚠️ **Link:** linktr.ee/rtg.bobby — this is fine for now but eventually point it to hyperfollow.com/bobbygalletta\n⚠️ **Old post still there:** \"On My Body\" single promo from September 2025 — that one slipped through. Go delete that too. It's got engagement from months ago and doesn't match your fresh start energy\n\n**Overall: 8/10.** The profile looks intentional and you can tell you're a real person who makes music and messes around with AI. \n\nGo delete that one leftover post and you're ready. Then we start posting. ⚡🕶️\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61163,"output":262,"cacheRead":19753,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774153221105}}
