{"type":"message","id":"241f4c22","parentId":"523db24a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:22:40.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's late at night (around midnight EST on Sunday). Bobby's asking what's good to post right now. It's not prime time but it's also not terrible - late night scrolling happens. Let me think about what would be good content right now.\n\nSome options:\n1. An intro post - \"fresh start on here, here's what I'm about\"\n2. Something about what he's currently working on\n3. A late night random thought\n4. Something about the tools he's using\n5. A take on something\n\nLet me draft a few options for him to choose from or just give him a few directions to pick from.","thinkingSignature":"10c30e123264398db29544e8624cdae30d634abc0fe07ee40403148c9aa105fb"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\nIt's midnight — not prime time but it's also not dead. People still scroll late at night. And you're not competing with the 9 AM crowd yet.\n\nHere's what I'd post **right now:**\n\n**Option 1 — The Intro**\n> \"fresh start on here. music, ai, faceless content, whatever i'm building that week. posting the process. knoxville, tn.\"\n> *That's it. Simple. Clean. People who vibe with it will follow.*\n\n**Option 2 — Late Night Realness**\n> \"it's midnight and i'm thinking about the ai tool i'm gonna use for next week's content. who's still up?\"\n> *Opens the door for engagement. People who are up will reply.*\n\n**Option 3 — Drop Something You're Working On**\n> \"new music coming soon. also working on something with ai that i've been experimenting with. stay tuned.\"\n> *Teases both sides of what you do. Builds anticipation.*\n\n---\n\n**My pick:** Option 1. The intro. Clean, simple, tells people who you are. Pin it for a week.\n\nPick one and I'll write the full post for you to copy-paste. Or give me your own direction and I'll draft it. ⚡🕶️\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniM