{"type":"message","id":"59a268ba","parentId":"783baa46","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:36:20.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compile what I found. Bobby's likes show a clear picture:\n\n**AI & Automation heavy:**\n- AI tools for making money\n- Autonomous AI agents for business (OpenClaw R&D department)\n- AI video/UGC automation\n- AI content monetization\n- His own Jarvis/clipping software experiments\n- App entrepreneurship ($80k/mo stories)\n\n**Some personal:**\n- Personal development / success mindset\n- His own product/AI data processor posts\n\n**Political/controversial:**\n- O'Keefe / election fraud expose\n- Iran war spending / Israel commentary\n- Some grumpy/aggressive comments\n\nThis is a really clear picture of Bobby's interests. I should present this to him.","thinkingSignature":"8ba826acda02d714a82590e5291207f9488fe4d5cccdbf6df03e80ffabf9bcf5"},{"type":"text","text":"Here's what your recent likes say about you:\n\n**🧠 AI & Automation (main vibe)**\n- \"OpenClaw R&D department\" — running 5 AI models that debate your business autonomously\n- \"Claude can run your ecom TikTok like a $500/hour social media manager\"\n- \"UGC industry is dead, AI killed it\" — adapting to AI content\n- $80k/mo app stories, $95k/mo AI health pages — AI monetization\n- \"Jarvis running 100 experiments on my clipping software\" — your own setup\n\n**💼 Entrepreneurship**\n- Building autonomous ad engines\n- App dev success stories\n- AI product architecture\n\n**🧪 Personal stuff you're into**\n- Your own Jarvis/clipping automation experiments\n- Personal development / success mindset\n\n**⚠️ Political/controversial (scattered in there)**\n- O'Keefe expose stuff\n- Iran war spending takes\n- Some edge political commentary\n\n---\n\n**What this tells me:** You're deep in the AI automation rabbit hole. Building your own tools, watching how others use AI to make money, and you're not shy about political takes. Your feed should reflect that.\n\nWant me to pull some of this together into a content strategy? ⚡🕶️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69769,"output":414,"cacheRead":19753,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89936,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774190165345}}
