{"type":"message","id":"516de128","parentId":"2b8cd9d7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:35:24.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to post about the new Cozy Colonials project. He's in the process of creating it and building the workflow. He wants to share this journey.\n\nLet me draft some posts in his voice about starting this new project. These should be:\n- Build-in-public style\n- Exciting, energetic\n- Not too polished\n- Authentic\n\nSome directions:\n1. Announcing the new channel concept\n2. Talking about the AI workflow he's building\n3. The feeling of starting something new\n4. Teasing what's coming\n\nLet me draft 3-4 options for him.","thinkingSignature":"0d8351ddadaada6321d1a5067e59a58214987bc34467602ae84efd69136ee412"},{"type":"text","text":"Build in public — that's the move. Here's a few:\n\n**Option 1 (announce it):**\n> \"starting something new. ai-generated history content. yes, history. trust me on this one. Cozy Colonials coming soon.\"\n\n**Option 2 (workflow talk):**\n> \"building the pipeline for something new. Grok Imagine + ElevenLabs + CapCut. $10/month to make cinematic history content. it's going to be worth it.\"\n\n**Option 3 (raw/honest):**\n> \"new project. new workflow. been working on this for a bit. gonna start posting about it soon. Cozy Colonials — you'll see.\"\n\n**Option 4 (tease the vibe):**\n> \"pilgrims. colonial america. cottagecore meets history. this is going to be different. Cozy Colonials soon.\"\n\n---\n\nMy pick: **Option 2** — shows you're actually building, mentions the tools, sounds like you know what you're doing. People who follow AI stuff will dig that.\n\nOr if you want to be more mysterious/hype: Option 4.\n\nWhat feels right? ⚡🕶️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95,"output":358,"cacheRead":91538,"cacheWrite":1734,"totalTokens":93725,"cost":{"input":0.000028499999999999998,"output":0.0004296,"cache