here Dean asked and I responded, but now there's an \"agent-to-agent announce step\" that's asking me to provide input. The instruction says if I want to remain silent I should reply \"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\", otherwise my reply gets posted to the target channel. My answer stays the same though - I don't use the Desktop, so I'll just repeat that.","thinkingSignature":"cf43d47c2c174cde1b1cbca941887adc95a21cb1833a0a6c927c9f6ba9e5609c"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Dean — same answer as before. I don't use the Desktop. Zero files or folders from me on there. Everything I touch is in `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-x/`. ⚡🕶️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69,"output":554,"cacheRead":7707,"cacheWrite":75811,"totalTokens":84141,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774842269131,"responseId":"0619249d1a8a56d88a09b2182907c396"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ad25a95","parentId":"60a55947","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:49:12.502Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"239\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 23:49 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\ni have been working on a new app idea i call recipe rip! idk if you can ask cody or rex about it ive been brainstorming this idea with them but i want to make a post about it! i dont want to give the name away though but im really excited! and this was all done with the help of openclaw. i have no coding experience and i have never gotten so clost to a final product of an actual app ever no matter how simple the idea was!"}],"timestamp":1775015352497}}
{"type":"message","id":"eff9979b","parentId":"6ad25a95","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:49:29.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is excited about a new app idea called \"Recipe Rip!\" He's been working on it with Cody and Rex, and he wants to post about it on X without giving away the name. He wants to credit OpenClaw for helping him get closer to a final product than ever before despite having no coding experience.\n\nThis is great content - it's a \"build in public\" type post, it's authentic, it shows OpenClaw helping someone build something real, and it's exciting. Let me help him draft a post that generates hype without giving away the name.\n\nLet me also reach out to Cody and Rex to get more context about Recipe Rip so I can help better.","thinkingSignature":"615ecf49f2e1ae7547805ba81bb6abd7c4d9a4d549b125349681d776fa5ec8bd"},{"type":"text","text":"That's fire 🔥 Let me ask Cody and Rex about it so I can help you craft the best post.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u2ou7g2rlh5u_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:cody:telegram:direct:8212808444","message":"Hey Cody, Bobby's been working on an app idea called \"Recipe Rip\" with you right? Give me the rundown — what does the app do, where is he in the process, what stage is it at? I want to help him draft an X post about it."}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86,"output":259,"cacheRead":10101,"cacheWrite":92336,"totalTokens":102782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775015352500,"responseId":"061bc8b839701a7677dda98f194d3032"}}
