rast:** \"I spent 5 minutes reading about someone's grandmother to find out how much flour to use. There has to be a better way.\"\n3. **The simple pitch:** \"Stop reading. Start cooking. — $6.99, one time.\"\n\n**Good hook for X:** \"Recipe blogs are designed to waste your time. We fixed that.\"\n\nWant me to draft some X post options for Bobby?"}],"timestamp":1775015471689,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:rex:telegram:direct:8212808444","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}}}
