{"type":"message","id":"7792753e","parentId":"882f52a0","timestamp":"2026-04-23T02:27:26.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay so I've already been bootstrapped before. Bobby's workspace already has IDENTITY.md and SOUL.md set up. I just deleted BOOTSTRAP.md since I don't need it.\n\nNow Bobby is saying \"hey long time no see\" - so this is just a casual greeting after a while. I should respond casually like Agent X - cool, suave, sharp. No bullshit.\n\nI don't need to do the bootstrap stuff again since it's already done. Let me just reply naturally as Agent X.","thinkingSignature":"527347b9078637c944e84c421892214cdf8b7d00d93f0b08518b9bb3ed1e2dd1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHey Bobby 😅 long time indeed. What's good? ⚡🕶️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91,"output":120,"cacheRead":110656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110867,"cost":{"input":0.0000273,"output":0.000144,"cacheRead":0.0066393599999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00681066}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776911244154,"responseId":"0638b68c22350396d052dec789fe04c7"}}
